---
import Heading from "./Heading.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-6">
        <Heading title="A Different Approach to Healthcare" subTitle="Who We Are">
            At St Catherine's Group, we believe that exceptional healthcare starts with
            truly understanding the individual. Our approach centres on building meaningful
            relationships with every person we work with, ensuring care that is as unique
            as you are.
        </Heading>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12">
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="w-18 h-18 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-green-dark flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                              d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-green-dark mb-3">Trusted Expertise</h3>
                <p class="text-green-dark leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-2xl">
                    Our team of qualified professionals brings years of experience
                    and a genuine commitment to your wellbeing.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="w-18 h-18 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-green-dark flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                              d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-green-dark mb-3">Collaborative Care</h3>
                <p class="text-green-dark leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-2xl">
                    We work alongside you and your support network to deliver
                    care that makes a real, lasting difference.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
